{
  "stem": "5970.2",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 113,
      "text": "But we knew there were a hundred of them.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 114,
      "text": "They brought us extra food whenever they could.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 115,
      "text": "And they were very good.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 116,
      "text": "They really helped us a lot.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 117,
      "text": "But the conditions in the camp and what was going on there was just something horrific.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 118,
      "text": "It was our first introduction to a concentration camp.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 119,
      "text": "And for the first time, we realized that people are being exterminated.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 120,
      "text": "There is a machine.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 121,
      "text": "There is a factory that kills people.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 122,
      "text": "This was the first time we came in contact with all these horrible things.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 123,
      "text": "There were a lot of the Russian civilian women there from the villages, very simple women.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 124,
      "text": "And their lot was very miserable.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 125,
      "text": "They were treated very badly.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 126,
      "text": "They were beaten day and night.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 127,
      "text": "And they didn't know what's happening.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 128,
      "text": "They couldn't understand a word of German.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 129,
      "text": "We all spoke German.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 130,
      "text": "So we knew, at least, what they wanted, as is impossible as it was, the tasks-- the tasks that we were given.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 131,
      "text": "But we knew what-- we could communicate with them.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 132,
      "text": "But they didn't understand a word of German.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 133,
      "text": "They couldn't speak Polish.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 134,
      "text": "And they were so miserable.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 135,
      "text": "They cried all the time.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 136,
      "text": "Whenever we came in touch with them, they were crying.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 137,
      "text": "They were terrible.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 138,
      "text": "There were a lot of the Russian prisoners of war as well, Russian men.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 139,
      "text": "We only saw them through the wire because we were separated from the men.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 140,
      "text": "But we didn't encounter any other people, Jewish people, at that stage.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 141,
      "text": "And these women told us that they exterminated there thousands of people.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 142,
      "text": "According to the statistics, in Majdanek, 750,000 people were killed in this crematorium there.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 143,
      "text": "So it's a horrible story.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 144,
      "text": "Now, we were put to work.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 145,
      "text": "And it was total chaos.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
